MOST IMMEDIATE
Nor55/1/1/CF-70
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of
Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 2nd July, 1970
11th Asadha, 1892.
The undersigned is directed to forward herewith a copy of the
Order of the President dated 2nd July 1970, appointing Shri K.C. Pant,
Minister of State in the Ministry of Home Affairs also as Minister of
State, Departments of Electronics and Scientific and Industrial Research
in the Cabinet Secretariat.
ughe
(R.N. Kalia)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/the
Joint Secretary to the Prine Minister Privato Secretary to the
Prime Minister.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(R.N.
Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission/Secretary, Union
Public Service Commission/Conptroller and Auditor General of
India, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the
Government of India/Lok Sapha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat/
Establishment Officer, Ministry of Home Af fairs, for information.
(R.N. Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
*JAISNAL*
250 Copies.
